  "texts": [
    "However, the respondents themselves highlighted the solution also.",
    "For example \"ChatGPT does not provide exact solutions to the queries or exact guidance on our problem.",
    "It is completely the user's responsibility to dig out and get the appropriate response from ChatGPT.",
    "But I admit if the user is capable, ChatGPT is a great tool to get facilitation for daily personal life matters and for work tasks\" (R-7)",
    "When asked about the integration of ChatGPT with the organizational knowledge base, respondents are of the view that when they think of ChatGPT integrated with the organizational system, and they would have a formal avenue to use it for work tasks, it gives them great feeling and satisfaction."
  ],
